---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Markdown from '../components/Markdown.astro';

const explainer = `
**AmicBridge is a private introduction desk for capital and opportunities.**

We quietly connect individuals who have capital with individuals and projects that need it.
No sign-ups, no public listings, no accounts to create — everything happens privately.

We never hold funds, arrange payments, or guarantee outcomes.  
Our role is limited to **information and introductions** between interested parties.

### How AmicBridge Works
1. You tell us discreetly what you need or what you offer.  
2. We search our private network for a suitable counterpart.  
3. If you want a direct connection, you unlock their details for a small fee.

All financial decisions, agreements, and transfers happen *outside* AmicBridge,  
strictly between you and the other party.

### What You Can Use AmicBridge For
– Private lending  
– Private borrowing  
– Property-related capital needs  
– Small business funding  
– Private co-investment opportunities  
– Connecting with people who prefer discretion over public marketplaces

AmicBridge is built on **privacy, discretion, and direct human connection**.
We stay outside the deal. You stay in full control.
`;
---

<Layout title="AmicBridge – Private Capital Connections">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="mb-10">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
      Discreet connections between capital and opportunity.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-2xl">
      A private desk for individuals seeking capital or offering it.  
      No platforms holding your money — just confidential introductions with real people.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN TEXT -->
  <section class="mb-10">
    <Markdown content={explainer} class="text-lg leading-relaxed" />
  </section>

  <!-- ACTION BUTTONS -->
  <section class="flex flex-wrap gap-6 mb-14">

    <!-- Need Capital -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+need+capital+through+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg"
    >
      I Need Capital
    </a>

    <!-- Have Capital -->
    <a 
      href="https://wa.me/4792928373?text=Hi%2C+I+have+capital+and+want+opportunities+via+AmicBridge"
      target="_blank"
      class="bg-rose-400 hover:bg-rose-500 text-slate-900 font-semibold px-12 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg"
    >
      I Have Capital to Deploy
    </a>

  </section>

  <!-- PRICING MODEL -->
  <section class="mt-8 max-w-2xl space-y-4">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">How You Pay AmicBridge</h2>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      AmicBridge does not take a percentage of your deal and never touches your money.
      You only pay for **private introductions**.
    </p>

    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-slate-300 space-y-1">
      <li>You message us privately via WhatsApp.</li>
      <li>We confirm whether we have a suitable match.</li>
      <li>You pay a small unlock fee to receive the direct contact details.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-slate-300">
      Unlock fee: <strong>499 NOK per contact</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
      Payments are handled directly with AmicBridge (e.g., Vipps to <strong>92928373</strong>).  
      AmicBridge never manages client funds and does not offer financial advice.  
      All agreements remain strictly between the private parties involved.
    </p>
  </section>

</Layout>
